These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-1::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  nurse, designer, manager
There are 3 different favourite colors: white, orange, chestnut
3 different games are played: domino, whist, poker
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: bellflower, zinnia, azalea
1. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the person playing poker##1
2. the person playing domino is on the left of the person who growsazalea##1
3. the nurse is between the person who likes orange and the person who likes chestnut##2
4. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the designer##1
5. the person playing poker is the person who likes orange##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |
| Job         | designer | nurse   | manager   |
| Color   | orange     | white | chestnut |
| Game   | poker  | domino    | whist      |
| Flower     | zinnia     | bellflower      | azalea |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-2::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: daisy, iris, begonia
3 different games are played: chess, backgammon, billiard
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, ritmeester, game
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: thriller, musical, adventure
1. the person playing billiard is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1
2. the game-smoker is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
3. the person who growsiris is the game-smoker##1
4. the person who growsdaisy is the ritmeester-smoker##1
5. the person watching thriller movies is between the person playing backgammon and the person who growsbegonia##2
6. the person who growsbegonia is the person watching musical movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3      |
| Flower          | iris  | daisy     | begonia     |
| Game   | backgammon     | billiard     | chess      |
| Cigar   | game  | ritmeester | bongani |
| Movie-Genre           | adventure | thriller     | musical       |

