.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-3::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: december, november, february
There are 3 different nationalities: german, american, russian
City: prague, miami, edinburgh
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: classical, r&b, techno
1. the german is on the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
2. the fan classical is between the russian and the person traveling to edinburgh##2
3. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far left##1
4. the fan r&b is the person who's birthday is in november##1
5. the fan classical is the person traveling to miami##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |
| Birthday          | december  | february     | november     |
| Nationality           | russian | german  | american   |
| City   | prague  | miami    | edinburgh |
| Music-Genre           | techno     | classical | r&b |

