.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-4::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: spy, comedy, action
There are 3 different favourite beverages: water, sprite, cola
There are 3 different nationalities: nigerian, colombian, dutch
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: february, january, april
1. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the colombian##1
2. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
3. the person watching action movies is between the person drinking sprite and the nigerian##2
4. the person watching comedy movies is the person who's birthday is in january##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |     2      |     3      |
| Movie-Genre    | spy       | action  | comedy   |
| Beverage     | sprite    | cola  | water |
| Nationality     | colombian   | dutch | nigerian        |
| Birthday   | april | february     | january      |

