.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-5::.
3 different games are played: whist, domino, go
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: august, may, july
The people use 3 different means of transport: skateboard, subway, ship
There are 3 different nationalities: indian, german, malaysian
1. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
2. the indian is between the person driving the ship and the person who's birthday is in july##2
3. the person who's birthday is in august is the german##1
4. the person playing whist is on the right of the person playing go##1
5. the indian is on the left of the person playing domino##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| Game          | go    | whist     | domino      |
| Birthday         | august | may | july |
| Transport   | ship  | subway       | skateboard       |
| Nationality           | german     | indian       | malaysian     |

