House: craftsman, futuristic, modern
1. the futuristic house is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
2. the person who growsmarigold is the person who's sport is basketball##1
3. the person driving the jet-ski is between the person who growsbegonia and the futuristic house##2
4. the person driving the roller is on the far right##1
5. the person who growsorchid is on the right of the craftsman house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |
| Flower          | begonia | orchid | marigold    |
| Sport         | tennis | climbing      | basketball |
| Transport   | tram   | jet-ski     | roller        |
| House           | craftsman      | modern       | futuristic      |

