.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-8::.
City: liverpool, prague, boston
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: sunflower, poppy, soccer-climbing
There are 3 different favourite colors: lavender, purple, brown
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: weightlifting, parkour, soccer
1. the person who likes brown is on the far left##1
2. the person traveling to prague is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
3. the person traveling to prague is on the left of the person who growssunflower##1
4. the person who likes lavender is between the person who growspoppy and the person traveling to boston##2
5. the person traveling to prague is the person who's sport is soccer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |     3      |
| City      | liverpool       | prague      | boston      |
| Flower         | poppy    | soccer-climbing | sunflower      |
| Color           | brown | lavender     | purple |
| Sport   | parkour     | soccer          | weightlifting       |

