1. the cain-smoker is between the person who growsmarigold and the person who growsdahlia##2
2. the art-deco house is on the right of the person playing whist##1
3. the person playing bridge is on the far left##1
4. the modern house is on the far left##1
5. the person who growspoppy is on the left of the ritmeester-smoker##1
6. the ritmeester-smoker is the person who growsmarigold##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |    3     |
| Game      | bridge      | whist | domino     |
| House          | modern   | cape-cod      | art-deco     |
| Flower   | dahlia  | poppy      | marigold |
| Cigar     | bluemaster | cain        | ritmeester     |

