.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-10::.
3 different pets are kept: cat, goldfish, goat
There are 3 different nationalities: spanish, indonesian, german
3 different games are played: snooker, scrabble, canasta
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, fanta, cola
1. the owner of the cat is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
2. the indonesian is between the spanish and the owner of the goldfish##2
3. the person playing canasta is the owner of the goat##1
4. the person playing scrabble is the german##1
5. the person drinking cola is on the left of the spanish##1
6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person playing scrabble##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |        2        |    3     |
| Pet       | goldfish       | goat       | cat    |
| Nationality         | german | indonesian | spanish |
| Game       | scrabble      | canasta         | snooker |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate        | cola            | fanta  |

