3. the person who likes lavender is in the middle##1
4. the person who likes lavender is between the person who growsbegonia and the person who growsdahlia##2
5. the owner of the rabbit is on the far left##1
6. the person who growsdahlia is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |      3      |
