3. the person who likes mauve is on the left of the person who likes turquise##1
4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
5. the person who's hobby is skydiving is between the person traveling to paris and the person who's birthday is in august##2
6. the person who's birthday is in december is the person who likes turquise##1

.:: Answer ::.
