3. the person traveling to hannover is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
4. the person who likes black is on the left of the old-henry-smoker##1
5. the person who likes mauve is the blend-smoker##1
6. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the person traveling to hannover##1

.:: Answer ::.
