.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-18::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: august, april, july
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: climbing, weightlifting, swimming
City: hamburg, berlin, rome
The people have 3 different hobbies: card-games, board-games, hiking
1. the person traveling to rome is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
2. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
3. the person who's sport is swimming is the person who's hobby is card-games##1
4. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
5. the person who's sport is climbing is on the far right##1
6. the person who's birthday is in july is between the person who's birthday is in august and the person traveling to berlin##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |    3     |
| Birthday           | april   | july   | august |
| Sport   | swimming | weightlifting   | climbing     |
| City   | berlin     | hamburg      | rome    |
| Hobby           | card-games | board-games | hiking    |

