3 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, dannemann, chaman
House: craftsman, cottage, farmhouse
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: orchid, iris, bellflower
1. the person who growsiris is the farmhouse house##1
2. the cottage house is on the left of the chaman-smoker##1
3. the craftsman house is between the person driving the skateboard and the vegafina-smoker##2
4. the cottage house is the person who growsbellflower##1
5. the person who growsorchid is between the person driving the trike and the cottage house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |      2      |      3      |
| Transport      | skateboard | bus     | trike        |
| Cigar         | dannemann   | chaman | vegafina |
| House   | cottage        | craftsman       | farmhouse      |
| Flower           | bellflower           | orchid    | iris       |

