.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-20::.
There are 3 different nationalities: german, american, polish
The people have 3 different hobbies: hiking, gardening, woodworking
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: metal, pop, folk
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: dahlia, rose, amaryllis
1. the german is on the right of the fan pop##1
2. the person who's hobby is gardening is the person who growsdahlia##1
3. the fan pop is the person who growsdahlia##1
4. the fan metal is the polish##1
5. the person who's hobby is woodworking is between the person who growsamaryllis and the fan pop##2
6. the fan folk is the german##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |
| Nationality        | american      | german | polish |
| Hobby         | gardening     | woodworking    | hiking        |
| Music-Genre       | pop | folk   | metal   |
| Flower   | dahlia          | rose     | amaryllis       |

 